1. Install Node.js - https://nodejs.org/en/
2. Install bower - npm install -g bower - http://bower.io/
3. Navigate to diectory where project will be held
4. Create your project directory - mkdir paoloMemesPolymer
5. Install your project with bower - bower init
6. Enter throught he bower prompts, first few will require some input, can enter through the rest
6a. Enter index.html as the main file
7. Install polymer - bower install --save Polymer/polymer
8. Open up your project with your favorite editor
9. Add an index.html file to the project root